rationale: Although there is little information on the species population status it is fairly widespread across a number of separate locations within its range. More survey is recommended but the species is assessed as Least Concern.
evaluator: Snoeks, J. (Freshwater Fish Red List Authority) & Darwall, W. (Freshwater Biodiversity Assessment Programme)
